@eirene_belle

My favorite comfort food in the autumn season. Freshly picked vegetables smell like heaven and I have chosen the perfect recipe for today, Moussaka! Moussaka is to the Greek what Lasagna is to Italians. A rich tomato meat sauce layered with eggplant instead of pasta sheets, and topped with a thick layer of b√©chamel sauce, this traditional Greek recipe takes time to assemble ‚Äì but it‚Äôs well worth the effort!Ingredients For the Meat Sauce ‚Ä¢ Extra virgin olive oil ‚Ä¢ Onion ‚Ä¢ Garlic cloves ‚Ä¢ Ground lamb or beef ‚Ä¢ Sea salt ‚Ä¢ Black pepper ‚Ä¢ Ground cinnamon ‚Ä¢ Ground nutmeg ‚Ä¢ Tomato paste ‚Ä¢ Crushed tomatoes ‚Ä¢ Dry red wine ‚Ä¢ Bay leaf For the Vegetables ‚Ä¢ Eggplants ‚Ä¢ Salt ‚Ä¢ Oil For the B√©chamel Sauce ‚Ä¢ All-purpose flour ‚Ä¢ Butter ‚Ä¢ Whole milk, warmed ‚Ä¢ Sea salt ‚Ä¢ Black pepper ‚Ä¢ Ground nutmeg ‚Ä¢ Parmesan cheese, grated ‚Ä¢ Egg yolk

‚ô¨ original sound - Irene

yt_dlp_info.description: My favorite comfort food in the autumn season. Freshly picked vegetables smell like heaven and I have chosen the perfect recipe for today, Moussaka! Moussaka is to the Greek what Lasagna is to Italians. A rich tomato meat sauce layered with eggplant instead of pasta sheets, and topped with a thick layer of b√©chamel sauce, this traditional Greek recipe takes time to assemble ‚Äì but it‚Äôs well worth the effort!Ingredients For the Meat Sauce ‚Ä¢ Extra virgin olive oil ‚Ä¢ Onion ‚Ä¢ Garlic cloves ‚Ä¢ Ground lamb or beef ‚Ä¢ Sea salt ‚Ä¢ Black pepper ‚Ä¢ Ground cinnamon ‚Ä¢ Ground nutmeg ‚Ä¢ Tomato paste ‚Ä¢ Crushed tomatoes ‚Ä¢ Dry red wine ‚Ä¢ Bay leaf For the Vegetables ‚Ä¢ Eggplants ‚Ä¢ Salt ‚Ä¢ Oil For the B√©chamel Sauce ‚Ä¢ All-purpose flour ‚Ä¢ Butter ‚Ä¢ Whole milk, warmed ‚Ä¢ Sea salt ‚Ä¢ Black pepper ‚Ä¢ Ground nutmeg ‚Ä¢ Parmesan cheese, grated ‚Ä¢ Egg yolk
